   Politics &amp; Policy:
   Crisis in the Mideast Adds an Unexpected Twist
   To Midterm Elections Already Considered Pivotal
   ----
   By David Shribman
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/04/90
</DATE>
